description:
Biden is leaving Americans on the ground in Afghanistan. Who is telling the President of the United States what questions he can and cannot answer? Clay and Buck honor our 13 fallen in Kabul. Fauci wants your kids to get the shot. Europeans are protesting against mandates harder than Americans. Parents turn to home schooling in wake of possible vaccine and mask mandates.
